---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SEOHead from '@/components/SEOHead.astro';
import OrganizationSchema from '@/components/schemas/OrganizationSchema.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <Fragment slot="seo">
    <SEOHead
      title="Apply Now | Free Loan Application | NIK Finance"
      description="Apply for a car loan, home loan, personal loan, or business finance in just 5 minutes. Free service with 130+ lenders. AI-powered matching for fast approval."
      keywords="apply for loan, free loan application, car loan application, home loan apply, personal loan apply, business loan apply, fast loan approval Australia"
      canonical="https://www.nik.finance/apply"
    />
  </Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="schema">
    <OrganizationSchema />
  </Fragment>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0d4d3e] to-[#1e3a5f] py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
        Apply Now
      </h1>
      <p class="font-paragraph text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
        Start your loan application in just a few minutes. Our AI-powered platform matches you with the best lenders from our panel of 130+ -- completely free of charge.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://app.middle.finance/ref/7d27aec6-deb1-4e44-8bd8-85f8f8aecff3"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 py-5 bg-[#10b981] text-white font-heading font-semibold rounded-2xl hover:bg-[#0d9668] transition-colors duration-200 text-lg shadow-lg shadow-[#10b981]/25"
      >
        Start Your Free Application
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Trust Badges -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Free Service -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-[#f8fafb] rounded-2xl p-6 border border-[#333333]/5">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#10b981]/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-[#10b981]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-[#333333]">100% Free Service</h3>
            <p class="font-paragraph text-sm text-[#333333]/60">No fees, no charges. We are paid by the lenders.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 5 Min Application -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-[#f8fafb] rounded-2xl p-6 border border-[#333333]/5">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#10b981]/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-[#10b981]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-[#333333]">5 Minute Application</h3>
            <p class="font-paragraph text-sm text-[#333333]/60">Quick and easy online form. Apply from anywhere.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 130+ Lenders -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-[#f8fafb] rounded-2xl p-6 border border-[#333333]/5">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#10b981]/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-[#10b981]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-[#333333]">130+ Lenders</h3>
            <p class="font-paragraph text-sm text-[#333333]/60">Access Australia's largest lender panel.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Happens Next Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-[#f8fafb]">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <p class="font-paragraph text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[#10b981] mb-3">How It Works</p>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#333333]">
          What happens next?
        </h2>
        <p class="font-paragraph text-lg text-[#333333]/70 max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-4">
          From application to approval, here is what you can expect when you apply through NIK Finance.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="relative bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 border border-[#333333]/5">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#0d4d3e] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <span class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-white">1</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-[#333333] mb-3">Submit Your Application</h3>
          <p class="font-paragraph text-[#333333]/70">Complete our simple online form with your basic details and loan requirements. It takes around 5 minutes.</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="relative bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 border border-[#333333]/5">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#0d4d3e] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <span class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-white">2</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-[#333333] mb-3">AI Lender Matching</h3>
          <p class="font-paragraph text-[#333333]/70">Our AI instantly analyses your profile against 130+ lender credit policies to find the best matches for your situation.</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="relative bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 border border-[#333333]/5">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#0d4d3e] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <span class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-white">3</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-[#333333] mb-3">Expert Review</h3>
          <p class="font-paragraph text-[#333333]/70">A dedicated finance specialist reviews the AI recommendations and provides personalised advice tailored to your goals.</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Step 4 -->
        <div class="relative bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 border border-[#333333]/5">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#0d4d3e] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <span class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-white">4</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-[#333333] mb-3">Approval & Settlement</h3>
          <p class="font-paragraph text-[#333333]/70">Once you select your preferred option, we handle the paperwork and guide you through to settlement. Some loans approved same day.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#333333] mb-6">
        Ready to get started?
      </h2>
      <p class="font-paragraph text-lg text-[#333333]/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
        Join thousands of Australians who have found the right loan through NIK Finance. Our service is free, there is no obligation, and you could be approved in as little as 14 minutes.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://app.middle.finance/ref/7d27aec6-deb1-4e44-8bd8-85f8f8aecff3"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 py-5 bg-[#10b981] text-white font-heading font-semibold rounded-2xl hover:bg-[#0d9668] transition-colors duration-200 text-lg shadow-lg shadow-[#10b981]/25"
      >
        Start Your Free Application
      </a>
      <p class="font-paragraph text-sm text-[#333333]/50 mt-4">No credit score impact. No obligation. 100% free.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-[#f8fafb]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <p class="font-paragraph text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[#10b981] mb-3">FAQ</p>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#333333]">
          Application FAQs
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl border border-[#333333]/5 overflow-hidden">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer p-6 font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-[#333333] hover:text-[#0d4d3e] transition-colors">
            <span>How long does the application take?</span>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#10b981] transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6">
            <p class="font-paragraph text-[#333333]/70">The online application takes approximately 5 minutes to complete. You will need basic information about your employment, income, and the type of loan you are looking for. Once submitted, our AI begins matching you with suitable lenders immediately.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl border border-[#333333]/5 overflow-hidden">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer p-6 font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-[#333333] hover:text-[#0d4d3e] transition-colors">
            <span>Is there really no cost?</span>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#10b981] transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6">
            <p class="font-paragraph text-[#333333]/70">Yes, our broking service is 100% free for borrowers. We are paid a commission by the lender when your loan settles. There are no hidden fees, no application fees, and no obligation. You are free to walk away at any time.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl border border-[#333333]/5 overflow-hidden">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer p-6 font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-[#333333] hover:text-[#0d4d3e] transition-colors">
            <span>Will applying affect my credit score?</span>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#10b981] transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6">
            <p class="font-paragraph text-[#333333]/70">Submitting an enquiry through our platform does not impact your credit score. A formal credit check is only conducted once you choose to proceed with a specific lender and provide your consent. We always inform you before any credit enquiry is made.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl border border-[#333333]/5 overflow-hidden">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer p-6 font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-[#333333] hover:text-[#0d4d3e] transition-colors">
            <span>What documents do I need?</span>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#10b981] transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6">
            <p class="font-paragraph text-[#333333]/70">To get started, you do not need any documents -- just your basic details. Once you are matched with a lender and wish to proceed, you may need to provide identification (such as a driver licence), proof of income (recent payslips or tax returns), and bank statements. Your dedicated finance specialist will guide you through exactly what is needed.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl border border-[#333333]/5 overflow-hidden">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer p-6 font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-[#333333] hover:text-[#0d4d3e] transition-colors">
            <span>How fast can I get approved?</span>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#10b981] transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6">
            <p class="font-paragraph text-[#333333]/70">Approval times vary depending on the loan type and lender. Car loans can be approved in as little as 14 minutes. Home loans typically take a few business days. Personal loans and business finance fall somewhere in between. Our team works to expedite every application.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Disclaimer -->
  <section class="py-8 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <p class="font-paragraph text-sm text-[#333333]/50">
        NIK Finance Pty Ltd (ACN 685 393 917) is a Credit Representative (No. 567387) of Finsure Finance & Insurance Pty Ltd (Australian Credit Licence 384704). All applications are subject to lender assessment and approval. Terms, conditions, fees and charges apply.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
